data.description: Location, Location, Location!!!!! Don't Miss this Great opportunity of owning your own ready built home in the Highly sought-after Torino Area!  This beautiful and almost new Home is just Minutes From I-95, very close to restaurants and shopping centers and next to the Mets Minor League Stadium. Your future Home is less than 1 year old and for your pleasure it is one of the only few 3-car garage homes in the community. This 3 Bedroom, 2 bathroom split style home comes with an extra room for office or entertainment. Property does not have HOA and or neighbors on the back of the property, which allows for a very private backyard to be enjoyed by you and your family. Property also includes Hurricane Graded Windows and shutters for your safety. DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY!!!!
